<p class="ayah 4-18" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَيْسَتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلتَّوْبَةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the acceptance of repentance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّيِّـَٔـاتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the evil deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَضَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">approaches</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَدَهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] death,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he says,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed I</span></span><