<p class="ayah 4-47" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(have) been given</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Book,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامِنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَزَّلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We (have) revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُصَدِّقًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">confirming</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَعَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن قَبْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[that]</span></span><span class="word staticWord