<p class="ayah 4-48" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(does) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَغْفِرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">forgive</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُشْرَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">partners be associated</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَغْفِرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but He forgives</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا دُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">other than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He wills.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar