Word"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Book</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْحِكْمَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and [the] wisdom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَءَاتَيْنَـٰهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and [We] gave them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّلْكًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a kingdom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَظِيمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">great.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/4:54" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="547"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>54<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 4-55" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمِنْهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are some) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمِنْهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are some) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَدَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">turned away</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَفَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and sufficient</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِجَهَنَّمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Hell</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَعِيرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as a) Blazing Fire.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/4:55" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="548"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>55<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
