<p class="ayah 4-57" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe[d]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the good deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَنُدْخِلُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We will admit them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَنَّـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) Gardens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will abide</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span>