span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُتِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">was ordained</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقِتَالُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the fighting,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَرِيقٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a group</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَخْشَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[they] fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّاسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَخَشْيَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">as (they) fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَشَدَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">more intense</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَشْيَةً‌ۚ</span><span class="en seco