<p class="ayah 4-78" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيْنَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Wherever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكُونُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُدْرِككُّمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will overtake you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] death</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">even if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بُرُوجٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">towers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّشَيَّدَةٍ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">lofty.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُصِبْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">befalls them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cl