cWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ عِندِ ٱللَّهِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) from Allah.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَالِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So what (is wrong)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) these</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَوْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا يَكَادُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they do not seem</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْقَهُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) understand</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَدِيثًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any statement.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/4:78" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="571"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>78<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 4-79" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">What(ever)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصَابَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">befalls you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصَابَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">befalls you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَيِّئَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) evil</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is) from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَّفْسِكَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">yourself.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quran